{"tid":1054169,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「聖戰新娘」英籍初生兒證實病逝","createTime":"2019-03-09T15:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T18:03:36.000Z","uid":51183,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b7d4f6407790e9b6a5384528acb3bcdea1825629","tid":1054169,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T15:53:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190309/59348037?fbclid=IwAR0DU2Dx-Fz6kxsYRFnLbA9FKWHMNwvQ_I1l0zXf2MiNZpAqr-XaBKK-bak\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190309%2F59348037%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0DU2Dx-Fz6kxsYRFnLbA9FKWHMNwvQ_I1l0zXf2MiNZpAqr-XaBKK-bak&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2JS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=4f27a94f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190309%2F59348037%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0DU2Dx-Fz6kxsYRFnLbA9FKWHMNwvQ_I1l0zXf2MiNZpAqr-XaBKK-bak&h=4b04c0d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190309/59348037?fbclid=IwAR0DU2Dx-Fz6kxsYRFnLbA9FKWHMNwvQ_I1l0zXf2MiNZpAqr-XaBKK-bak</a><br />\n<br />\n【被拒返英】「聖戰新娘」英籍初生兒證實病逝 <del>人權組織</del>左膠：政府要負責<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n離家出走到敍利亞當「聖戰新娘」而被褫奪國籍的英國19歲少女貝古姆（Shamima Begum）目前身在難民營，敍利亞民主力量（Syrian Democratic Forces，SDF）發言人表示，她的初生兒子周四因肺炎死亡。<br />\n<br />\n貝古姆上月誕下兒子後，母子在SDF設立的難民營中生活，根據醫療文件顯示，她的兒子出生後不足三周便因肺炎死亡。貝古姆2015年與兩位朋友離家出走，赴敍利亞加入極端組織「伊斯蘭國」（IS）當 「聖戰新娘」，她欲帶同初生兒子歸國時，英國內政部決定褫奪她的公民身份。<br />\n<br />\n人權組織「庫爾德紅新月」（Kurdish Red Crescent）向英國廣播公司表示，貝古姆的兒子名為賈拉（Jarrah），周四早上因為呼吸困難與母親一起被送到醫院中，但在當地時間下午1時半死亡。貝古姆隨後返回難民營，其兒子於周五下葬，她的27歲荷蘭籍IS戰士丈夫雷代克（Yago Riedijk）現被囚在附近監獄中，已獲知會兒子的死訊。<br />\n<br />\n內政大臣賈偉德（Sajid Javid）對嬰兒去世表示同情，「可悲的是，可能有很多孩子出生在這個戰區，他們顯然是完全無辜的&hellip;&hellip;這件事提醒我們，這個戰區對所有人來說都非常危險」。<br />\n<br />\n由於貝古姆是在被褫奪國籍前誕子，故她的兒子仍然屬於英籍。貝古姆的朋友、前倫敦警察局局長巴布（Dal Babu）說：「作為一個國家，我們未能保護這個孩子，這位英國公民的死亡是完全可以避免的，她的家人向內政部要求協助，內政部卻回應說，你們來錯了部門。」<br />\n<br />\n救助兒童會政策主管麥克尼爾（Kirsty McNeill）認為，所有與IS有關的兒童都是衝突的受害者，認為男嬰及其他孩子的死亡都是可以避免的，「英國和其他原籍國必須對敍利亞東北部的公民負責」。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司 <br />\n<br />\n蒙阿拉寵召 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7671eaacd1dca6edab465826e68a1f0e0d4078","tid":1054169,"uid":125168,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T15:57:55.000Z","msg":"連個仔都死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後一張可能番到英國嘅牌都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922959b153d43f6f1f98b559e96e8258485d4259","tid":1054169,"uid":121146,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T16:11:07.000Z","msg":"咁細個就可以上天堂食處女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753fea90e14796eaeb46bf913b1599dad7f38000","tid":1054169,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T16:12:57.000Z","msg":"本來係一星R咭，之後可以有機會五星SSR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5813e1dafc4ab4c7073250a26c41cc0f668d452e","tid":1054169,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T16:18:38.000Z","msg":"兒童係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd55ce4856c03e24a7d6c9d1b23b79ecf2a59c8","tid":1054169,"uid":28913,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"5813e1dafc4ab4c7073250a26c41cc0f668d452e","tid":1054169,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T16:18:38.000Z","msg":"兒童係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T16:21:14.000Z","msg":"怪就怪自己老豆老母戇鳩"},{"pid":"e46ae87d097ce7c392b6e1be61808e39f417a285","tid":1054169,"uid":30710,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T17:18:36.000Z","msg":"老母正垃圾有乜計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\